data.description: Luxurious Executive Home on Expansive Wooded Lot - Your Dream Home Awaits!  Welcome to your new haven! This stunning executive home offers a perfect blend of elegance, functionality, and natural beauty. Boasting 3 spacious bedrooms, a full-sized office, a music room or den, 3.5 bathrooms, and a fully finished basement, this residence is a true gem.  Picturesque Outdoor Oasis: Situated on a sprawling 1.56-acre wooded lot, the natural beauty surrounding this home is simply breathtaking. Step onto the large mahogany deck overlooking the fenced backyard and immerse yourself in the vibrant foliage. The 15-zoned irrigation system ensures that this outdoor masterpiece is impeccably maintained.  Gourmet Kitchen and Inviting Spaces: The first floor features a chef's kitchen with an abundance of cabinets, a long island with additional seating, and a bright breakfast nook offering scenic views of the backyard. The kitchen seamlessly opens to a cozy family room with a gas fireplace, built-in speakers, and a unique "music room" – a perfect retreat for music, movies, or video games.  Entertainment-Ready Dining Room: Host your favorite holiday meals in the dining room, featuring wooden French doors, beautiful hardwood floors, and large windows. The first floor is completed by a half bathroom and a convenient laundry room.  Spacious Bedrooms and Private Sanctuary: Upstairs, the primary bedroom awaits with a large walk-in closet and a luxurious bathroom, complete with a deep soaking tub, separate shower, and a private water closet. Two additional spacious bedrooms, an office with cathedral ceilings, and a well-designed full bathroom provide ample space for everyone.  Finished Basement and Thoughtful Upgrades: The full finished basement offers additional living space, including a full bathroom. The 3-car garage, finished with drywall and gel coat floors, provides both practicality and style. A dedicated room for the water system and water heater adds convenience.  Upgrades for Peace of Mind: Recent upgrades, including a new roof with skylights in 2020, a new well pump in 2022, and leaf guard gutters, ensure that this home stands out as a top choice.  Your Dream Home Awaits - Call for Your Private Tour Today!
